/* --- PERFORMANCE MODULE & BENDER SECTION --- */
/*
.p- **Performance Module**:
    - **Vertical Organization**: Reorganize into three distinct, non-overlapping rows:
        1. **Knobs**: `PORT`, `TUNE`, `VOLUME`.
        2. **Switches**: `PORTAMENTO ON/OFF` and `POLY I / II`.
        3. **Dedicated Octave Zone**: A new section at the bottom for Octave buttons.
    - **Octave Zone Layout**:
        - Horizontal order: `OCT+` label, then two square buttons, then `OCT-` label.
        - Buttons: Both buttons must be the same color (standard grey `sq` style).
        - Labels: White, 9px Microgramma font, positioned on the sides of the button pair.
    - **Knob Labels**: Reduced to 9px Microgramma for a cleaner look.
    - **Poly Buttons**: Keep clean (no inner text).
- **Bender Section**:
    - **LFO TRIG**: Convert to a standard grey `sq` button (pulsador).
    - **LFO TRIG Label**: Position the text "LFO TRIG" directly above the button.
    - **Alignment**: Sliders and Trigger button in the same row.
    - **Positioning**: Moved bender stick slightly lower.
*/

.performance-module {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 10px 0 5px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: space-between;
    /* Distribute rows equally */
    background: transparent;
    border-top: 2px solid var(--black);
    margin-top: 0;
}

.perf-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 10px 0;
    position: relative;
    align-items: flex-start;
    /* Ensure labels are at the same top level */
}

.perf-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

.port-col {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    /* Space between label and switch */
}

.poly-col {
    flex: 2;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    /* Space between label and buttons */
}

.port-col .sw-unit {
    height: 54px;
    /* Matches asset height to align with buttons */
    margin-top: 2px;
}

.port-col .sw-path,
.port-col .sw-peg {
    height: 54px;
}

.sw-lbl {
    font-family: 'Microgramma', sans-serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.poly-col .main-lbl {
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.poly-buttons {
    display: flex;
    width: 100%;
    justify-content: space-around;
    padding-top: 5px;
    align-items: flex-start;
